The paper discusses attacks on physical layer cryptography schemes based on massive MIMO, which involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), cryptography (cs.CR), networking (cs.NI), and signal processing (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the advantages and limitations of different precoding schemes, which could fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SI).
